                              <label class="w3-text-grey"><br>Please fill in where you were certified as a Trainer and when, </br></label>
                              <label class="w3-text-teal"><b>Shcool Name</b></label>
                              <input class="w3-input w3-border w3-light-grey w3-round-xlarge"" id="schoolName-Input" name="schoolName" type="text" required></p>
                              <label id="errorMsg-sn" style="font-size: 14px; color: red" ><b>The school name where you have been certified must contain only letters  </br></label>
